## Open Questions

> [!QUESTION]
> **Data Storage Options:** How would you like the data to be saved?
> 1. **Local Storage:** The simplest option, but data is only saved on the device/browser you are using.
> 2. **Cloud Storage (e.g., JSONBlob or Firebase):** Allows you to access the fee data across multiple devices. (I noticed in your past projects you've used JSONBlob and Firebase for syncing). 
